				Just a personal note.  <BR>
<BR>
I have killed Hadden a total of 12 times over the last several months.  I have yet to see an earring drop.  At this point I'm feeling quite frustrated.  A few weeks ago I camped Hadden steadily for about 36 hours.  I found that the spawn time is indeed about 5 and a half hours, perhaps a bit longer at times but never over 6 hours.  I managed to kill him 6 times during that session without luck.  I gave up the camp to a very nice person who got the earring on his first kill.  I have had enough of Hadden.  I wish everyone else better luck than I have had with this camp.<BR>
